             description="Annotates Sentences based upon an OpenNLP model.",
             dependencies=SECTION,

public final class ThreadSafeSentenceDetector
extends SentenceDetector
    Normally I would use composition and a singleton, but here extension is done for @ConfigurationParameter discovery. Made a singleton mostly for model memory.
